README.md

Awesome

   [https://camo.githubusercontent.com/62e0cedf6ab0e2069507d122b18034dc61a
   fb552/687474703a2f2f7777772e6c6578616c6f66666c652e636f6d2f6766782f70385
   f6a656c70692e676966]PICO-8
   [https://camo.githubusercontent.com/f71a5c862f2ffa59183aefe9f908164c871
   1eaa3/687474703a2f2f7777772e6c6578616c6f66666c652e636f6d2f6766782f70385
   f747261636b65722e676966]tools
   [https://camo.githubusercontent.com/27ba321518f3aa089d16ece8088f06887d6
   cd64a/687474703a2f2f7777772e6c6578616c6f66666c652e636f6d2f6766782f70385
   f636173742e676966]code

   A curated list of PICO-8 resources, tutorials, tools and more. Inspired
   by the [https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome?1]awesome list thing.
   You might also like
   [https://github.com/LewisJEllis/awesome-lua]awesome-lua and
   [https://github.com/JanWerder/awesome-love2d]awesome-love2d.

   PICO-8 is a fantasy console for making, sharing and playing tiny games
   and other computer programs. When you turn it on, the machine greets
   you with a shell for typing in a subset of [http://www.lua.org/]Lua
   commands and provides simple built-in tools for creating your own
   cartridges.

